NAME
    Acme::AliG - Translates from English to Ali G

VERSION
    version 0.0102

SYNOPSIS
        echo hello | alig

    The above command will print 'allo'.

DESCRIPTION
    This module provides a script called alig. It will translate whatever
    you feed it via STDIN from English to Ali G.

AUTHOR
